    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of naturally aspirated precision, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power distribution. This chassis has been fastidiously maintained, showing no signs of subframe stress fractures, and has received proactive rod bearing service. The suspension retains its factory-correct damping rates and bushings, preserving the communicative steering rack and neutral handling balance. With its original paint depth and an interior free of typical soft-touch wear, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the purist collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
